{"title":"寒假复习计划","date":"2020-01-14T11:31:03.000Z","link":"2020/01/14/checkin/plan1","comments":true,"tags":["Daily check in"],"categories":["个人计划"],"updated":"2020-01-04T12:21:57.421Z","content":"<h2 id=\"寒假复习计划\">寒假复习计划<a href=\"2020/01/14/checkin/plan1#寒假复习计划\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"年前-年后\">年前 年后<a href=\"2020/01/14/checkin/plan1#年前-年后\"></a></h3><ol>\n<li>高等数学：基础巩固 做题形成知识体系   复习加回顾体系 主要的时间在 上午做题整理知识点</li>\n<li>下午： 算法 准备pat  + 专业课 </li>\n<li>晚上：播客整理</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"假期过年\">假期过年<a href=\"2020/01/14/checkin/plan1#假期过年\"></a></h3><ol>\n<li>Linux 基础使用 + 院校确定</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"关于时间作息安排\">关于时间作息安排<a href=\"2020/01/14/checkin/plan1#关于时间作息安排\"></a></h3><p>调整时间作息，尽量早起，时间更新待定</p>\n","next":{"title":"学期总结以及一月份打卡集合","link":"2020/01/01/checkin/Jan20"},"plink":"http://www.zqynn.cn/2020/01/14/checkin/plan1/","toc":[{"title":"寒假复习计划","id":"寒假复习计划","index":"1","children":[{"title":"年前 年后","id":"年前-年后","index":"1.1"},{"title":"假期过年","id":"假期过年","index":"1.2"},{"title":"关于时间作息安排","id":"关于时间作息安排","index":"1.3"}]}],"copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"http://www.zqynn.cn/2020/01/14/checkin/plan1/\" title=\"寒假复习计划\">http://www.zqynn.cn/2020/01/14/checkin/plan1/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}